<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko" data-theme="gym-light">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>GymHelper - 로그인</title>
    <%- include("partials/themeHeadScript") %>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/stylesheets/app.css">
</head>
<body class="auth-bg">
  <div class="relative isolate flex min-h-screen items-center justify-center overflow-hidden p-4 sm:p-6">
    <div class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-0 -z-10 bg-[radial-gradient(circle_at_15%_20%,color-mix(in_oklab,var(--color-primary)_16%,transparent)_0%,transparent_42%),radial-gradient(circle_at_88%_8%,color-mix(in_oklab,var(--color-accent)_14%,transparent)_0%,transparent_44%)]"></div>

    <div class="absolute right-4 top-4 z-10 sm:right-6 sm:top-6">
      <button type="button" class="btn btn-sm border border-base-300 bg-base-100/85 backdrop-blur" data-theme-toggle>
        <span class="text-xs">테마</span>
        <span data-theme-label class="badge badge-ghost badge-sm">다크</span>
      </button>
    </div>

    <section class="auth-panel card w-full max-w-[980px] overflow-hidden border border-base-300 bg-base-100/90 shadow-2xl">
      <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-[minmax(0,0.92fr)_minmax(0,1.08fr)]">
        <aside class="hidden border-r border-base-300/70 bg-base-200/35 p-8 lg:flex lg:flex-col lg:justify-between">
          <div class="space-y-4">
            <p class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.24em] text-primary">GymHelper</p>
            <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold leading-tight">운동 기록과 성장 지표를<br>한곳에서 관리하세요</h1>
            <p class="text-sm text-base-content/70">대시보드, 캘린더, 커뮤니티를 연결해 일관된 루틴을 유지할 수 있습니다.</p>
          </div>

          <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-base-content/80">
            <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="h-1.5 w-1.5 rounded-full bg-secondary"></span>월간 부위별 통계</li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="h-1.5 w-1.5 rounded-full bg-secondary"></span>운동 캘린더 기록</li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="h-1.5 w-1.5 rounded-full bg-secondary"></span>커뮤니티 피드백 공유</li>
          </ul>
        </aside>

        <div class="card-body gap-5 p-6 sm:p-8">
          <div class="space-y-2 text-center lg:text-left">
            <p class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-primary lg:hidden">GymHelper</p>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-balance">로그인</h2>
            <p class="text-sm text-base-content/70">계정으로 로그인해 루틴 기록을 이어서 관리하세요.</p>
          </div>

          <form class="login-form space-y-3" onsubmit="event.preventDefault(); login();">
            <label class="form-control w-full">
              <span class="label-text pb-1 text-sm font-medium">아이디</span>
              <input type="text" name="username" id="username" required class="input input-bordered w-full" placeholder="아이디를 입력하세요">
            </label>

            <label class="form-control w-full">
              <span class="label-text pb-1 text-sm font-medium">비밀번호</span>
              <input type="password" name="password" id="password" required class="input input-bordered w-full" placeholder="비밀번호를 입력하세요">
            </label>

            <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary mt-2 w-full">로그인</button>
          </form>

          <div class="divider my-0">또는</div>

          <a href="/signUp" class="btn btn-ghost w-full">회원가입</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </div>

  <script src="/javascripts/theme.js"></script>
  <script src="/javascripts/feedback.js"></script>
  <script src="/javascripts/apiClient.js"></script>
  <script src="/javascripts/logIn.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
